	<p>Radiant Cure isnt a bad purchase, particularly on a PvP server. I have it and use it to clear Tash, Disease and Poison DOTs, and it'll remove Malo as well (although for some reason, I can only clear Malo when I cast it on myself, but cant clear it if someone else casts it on me). I only have RC1, but plan to get RC2 when I get some more extra points.<br />
<br />
Going to get Virulent Paralysis soon, since all the melees in my guild curse whenever the topic of VP comes up. <img src="images/smilies/tongue.gif" border="0" alt="" title="stick out tongue" smilieid="6" /></p>
	
	
	
