	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>RC's main use imho is for getting rid of roots/snares and other magic based debuffs (Ala malo) that can't be cured by regular poison/disease cures.  Level 1 is horridly unreliable, don't count on it to save you when your rooted, because it probably won't.  Level 2 is a lot more reliable though and its saved my tail several times.  Its not 100% reliable though.<br />
<br />
The curse counter element of it is just too small and too long a reuse to be much use other than quickly clearing a few ssra trap aoes if they get set off.</p>
	
	
	
