</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I use VP almost all the time instead of a regular root.  The only time I bring up a regular root is when I know I'm going to be doing a lot of crowd control.  I have VP 1, and it lasts a decent amount of time.  My understanding is that VP 2 &amp; 3 only improve duration, and nothing else.<br />
<br />
That said, the knockback feature of VP is so useful that I prefer it to regular roots whenever I can.  The only drawback is the 2 min recast delay, but for most situations, that's sufficient.</p>
	
	
	
