Abolish disease removes 36 disease counters. Radiant Cure 1 removes just 9, and Radiant Cure 3 removes just 16. Maybe you mean that Radiant removes some dots that are not disease or poison, like Pyrocuror, Splurt, etc. But I doubt it can remove more disease dots than Abolish Disease does.</p>
	
	
	
